'''Rubyflame Lake''' was a [[lake]] located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Centares/Legends|Centares]].

Located near [[Muracie]], Rubyflame Lake's waters possessed a red glow as a result of running above an active lava flow. When the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] tapped the planet's accessible lava flows to produce geothermal power, the lake suffered. Within ten years it was corrupt with deadly acids and toxic chemicals.<ref name="marvel29">[[Star Wars (1977) 29|''Star Wars'' (1977) 29]]</ref>

